                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 153.)I took the prisoner, and have the soap.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I did not have it—the prosecutor picked it off the floor.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
